[quote=“R O F L, post:3, topic:96788”][quote author=soadfreek409 link=topic=139461.msg1341089#msg1341089 date=1179598919]
Do you have MSN? It would be much easier to explain on there…[br][size=1]Posted on: May 19, 2007, 06:51:53 AM[/size][hr]1. You need to forward a port on your router.
2. You need to set up the new JDK if you haven’t already
3. You need to compile.

These are usually really easy to find in the TuT section… Mod Taharok had an excellent TuT on making a full server, but I have no idea where it went hehe…
[/quote] Actually, you dont have to port forward.You can just use hamachi.But no-ip powns hamachi. If you want to code doggy, look for tutorial list some things what you want to add.[/quote]
